{"tid":1283223,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如果死夠十個示威者，香港民主自由就會自己解鎖。","createTime":"2019-07-03T17:54:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T21:59:25.000Z","uid":63118,"like":9,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"717fd4041e64d495aa7e9379de2c4f1f2a6300fe","tid":1283223,"uid":63118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T17:54:50.000Z","msg":"我相信有好多人仆出黎爭住做烈士<br />\n100個、1000個都唔成問題<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但大家要睇清楚，政府根本唔care</span><br />\n最後痛心嘅只會係家人、朋友、其他一齊付出嘅兄弟姊妹<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔好再咁傻喇！<br />\n大家一齊走落去先係對身邊嘅人負責任嘅做法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每多一個人出黎 對現場嘅人黎講係一份安心 多一份動力<br />\n我相信去過現場嘅人都好了解呢個心情<br />\n<br />\n成個活動先可以持之以恆爭取落去<br />\n所以少你一個就真係少好多 諗開啲 有咩想傾大把義士肯同你分擔<br />\n<br />\n共勉之<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7f9895dcde97da9397c7ba9194fe9a947ddc5c4","tid":1283223,"uid":63118,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T18:00:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f47c52529f96bb3458df1c1f3161cef7e5a80e20","tid":1283223,"uid":63118,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T18:00:58.000Z","msg":"有冇人想傾下計"},{"pid":"aa7a12afdd03444fdab752e7d96deaee09b87713","tid":1283223,"uid":63118,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T18:01:21.000Z","msg":"邊個負皮走左去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe1fb305854bada535b1d0a35aa5a4aadcd605d8","tid":1283223,"uid":20908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T18:02:04.000Z","msg":"係呀，跟本正苦就理9