ding up the launchers<br />\nFor the tear gas grenades<br />\nWe can take off our bandanas (for a moment)<br />\nAnd kiss behind the barricades//<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/a7NF7Hkrfxw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fa7NF7Hkrfxw&d=U4JEvS4lHdpitRbH3ga0O%2FcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=71fa8153\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/a7NF7Hkrfxw</a>"},{"pid":"88e841b282ea6490152c47c83fa06bab8f058604","tid":1283223,"uid":236878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa7a12afdd03444fdab752e7d96deaee09b87713","tid":1283223,"uid":63118,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T18:01:21.000Z","msg":"邊個負皮走左去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T21:59:25.000Z","msg":"用下腦得唔得?<br />\n個標題改到咁撚負面"}]}